V0404_01_00_00_0.text: Challenging me is your first mistake!

V0404_01_00_01_0.text: If you want to lose, you came to the right spot!

V0404_01_00_02_0.text: For the first time in forever, I'm facing a worthy opponent!

V0404_01_00_03_0.text:
Duel Disk! Go!
Duel Gazer! Let's roll!

V0404_01_00_04_0.text: I cooked up a special strategy to defeat you, Kite!

V0404_01_00_05_0.text: Just because we're family doesn't mean I'll go easy on ya!

V0404_01_00_06_0.text: It'll be my pleasure to take you down!

V0404_01_00_07_0.text: Did you forget the face of your #1 fan?

V0404_01_00_08_0.text:
Ooh, a Number!
This should be fun!

V0404_01_00_09_0.text:
I won't stop until I bust all the Barians!
Time for payback!

V0404_01_00_10_0.text:
I know you.
You're the Barian who's gonna lose to me!

V0404_03_00_04_0.text: All you're doing is firing me up!

V0404_03_00_05_0.text: Time to take off the kiddie gloves!

V0404_05_00_00_0.text:
I can still win!
As long as I don't give up!

V0404_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0404_08_00_00_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Aqua Jet!

V0404_08_00_01_0.text:
I activate my Spell!
Xyz Gift!

V0404_08_00_01_1.text: I use 2 Overlay Units to draw 2 cards!

V0404_08_00_02_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Overlay Regen!

V0404_08_00_02_1.text: This card turns into an Xyz Monster's Overlay Unit!

V0404_08_00_03_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Mystical Space Typhoon!

V0404_08_00_03_1.text: It destroys a Spell or Trap Card on the field!

V0404_08_00_04_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Salvage!

V0404_08_00_04_1.text: I retrieve 2 WATER monsters with 1500 or lower ATK!

V0404_08_00_05_0.text: The Continuous Spell, Different Dimension Deepsea Trench!

V0404_08_00_05_1.text: When this card activates, I banish 1 WATER monster!

V0404_08_00_06_0.text: Different Dimension Deepsea Trench's effect activates!

V0404_08_00_06_1.text: I Special Summon the monster that this card banished!

V0404_08_00_07_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Falling Current!

V0404_08_00_07_1.text: I can change a monster's Level to a number between 1 and 3!

V0404_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Monster Reborn!

V0404_08_00_08_1.text: I Special Summon a monster from the Graveyard!

V0404_08_00_09_0.text: I activate the Continuous Spell, Sea Lord's Amulet!

V0404_08_00_09_1.text: Effects can't destroy the WATER monsters on my field!

V0404_08_00_10_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Surface!

V0404_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Secret Retaliation!

V0404_08_00_11_1.text: You can't hunt a shark when the shark's hunting you!

V0404_08_00_12_1.text: I activate my Spell Card, Chain Summon!

V0404_08_00_13_0.text: I put out the bait, and you chomped right into it!

V0404_08_00_13_1.text: The Trap Card, Xyz Dimension Splash!

V0404_08_00_14_0.text:
Heh!
I caught me a big one!

V0404_08_00_14_1.text: I activate the Trap, Splash Capture!

V0404_08_00_15_0.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, Bubble Bringer!

V0404_08_00_16_1.text: I send this card to the Graveyard to revive two monsters!

V0404_08_00_17_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Fish Rain!

V0404_08_00_17_1.text: I Special Summon a monster from my hand!

V0404_08_00_18_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Icy Crevasse!

V0404_08_00_18_1.text: When an effect destroys my monster, I destroy one of yours!

V0404_08_00_19_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Poseidon Wave!

V0404_08_00_19_1.text: This card negates your monster's attack!

V0404_08_00_20_0.text: I activate the Trap, Torrential Reborn!

V0404_08_00_20_1.text: It resurrects my WATER monsters and deals you damage!

V0404_08_00_21_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Torrential Tribute!

V0404_08_00_21_1.text: All monsters on the field are destroyed!

V0404_08_00_22_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Dimensional Prison!

V0404_08_00_23_0.text:
I activate my Counter Trap!
Seven Tools of the Bandit!

V0404_08_00_23_1.text: I pay 1000 LP to negate and destroy a Trap!

V0404_08_00_24_0.text: Since you activated a Trap, I can activate Explosive Urchin!

V0404_08_00_25_0.text: Explosive Urchin's effect deals you damage!

V0404_09_00_00_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Cat Shark's effect!

V0404_09_00_00_1.text: An Xyz Monster gains ATK and DEF this turn!

V0404_09_00_01_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Shark Fortress's effect!

V0404_09_00_01_1.text:
My chosen monster gains an extra attack!
Mayhem Missiles!

V0404_09_00_02_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Bahamut Shark's effect!

V0404_09_00_03_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Black Ray Lancer's effect!

V0404_09_00_04_0.text: Full Armored Black Ray Lancer destroys your Spell or Trap!

V0404_09_00_05_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Shark Caesar's effect!

V0404_09_00_06_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Aero Shark's effect!

V0404_09_00_07_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Leviathan Dragon's effect!

V0404_09_00_08_0.text: Embodiment of Punishment uses an Overlay Unit!

V0404_09_00_08_1.text: Your monsters switch to Attack Position and have to attack!

V0404_09_00_09_1.text: It can attack again by reviving and weakening your monster!

V0404_09_00_10_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Shark Drake Veiss's effect!

V0404_09_00_10_1.text: A monster's ATK and DEF drop to 0 for the rest of this turn!

V0404_09_00_11_0.text: Hope Woven Dragon Spider Shark's effect activates!

V0404_09_00_11_1.text: It uses 1 Overlay Unit to lower your monsters' ATK!

V0404_09_00_12_0.text: Spider Shark's leaving you a parting gift!

V0404_09_00_13_1.text: It transforms a Level 3 WATER monster into an Overlay Unit!

V0404_09_00_14_0.text: Nightmare Shark uses an Overlay Unit to activate its effect!

V0404_09_00_15_1.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to increase its ATK!

V0404_09_00_16_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Crystalzero's effect!

V0404_09_00_17_0.text: I activate Full Armored Crystalzero Lancer's effect!

V0404_09_00_17_1.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to negate all your monsters' effects!

V0404_09_00_18_0.text: When Xyz Remora is Special Summoned, its effect activates!

V0404_09_00_19_0.text: If Megalodon deals battle damage, it can destroy a monster!

V0404_09_00_20_0.text: By Special Summoning Kaiser Sea Snake, its effect activates!

V0404_09_00_21_1.text: I choose a monster and summon a Fish with the same Level!

V0404_09_00_22_0.text: Friller Rabca's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0404_09_00_23_0.text: Summoning a Fish, Sea Serpent or Aqua means I can play this!

V0404_09_00_24_0.text: When Shocktopus is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0404_09_00_24_1.text: The equipped monster has 0 ATK and can't change positions!

V0404_09_00_25_0.text: When Skull Kraken is summoned, it destroys a face-up Spell!

V0404_09_00_26_0.text: Skull Kraken can change battle positions once per turn!

V0404_09_00_27_1.text: All Starfish on my field gain a Level!

V0404_09_00_28_0.text: Spear Shark's effect activates when it's summoned!

V0404_09_00_30_0.text: When Double Fin Shark is summoned, its effect activates!

V0404_09_00_31_0.text: When Double Shark is summoned, I can activate its effect!

V0404_09_00_32_1.text: I Tribute it to destroy a Spell or Trap Card!

V0404_09_00_33_0.text: Depth Shark uses its effect to gain ATK this turn!

V0404_09_00_34_0.text: By reviving Tripod Fish, its effect activates!

V0404_09_00_35_0.text: When Drill Barnacle deals direct damage, it gains ATK!

V0404_09_00_36_0.text: When Needle Sunfish swims away, it lowers a monster's ATK!

V0404_09_00_37_1.text: I reduce its Level to play a Level 3 or lower WATER monster!

V0404_09_00_38_0.text: When Big Jaws attacks, it's banished at the end of battle!

V0404_09_00_39_0.text: When Big Whale is Tribute Summoned, its effect activates!

V0404_09_00_39_1.text: I Special Summon three Level 3 WATER monsters from my deck!

V0404_09_00_40_0.text: When I summon Right Hand Shark, I can draw Left Hand Shark!

V0404_09_00_41_0.text: I Special Summon Right Hand Shark from my Graveyard!

V0404_09_00_42_1.text: I Special Summon a WATER monster between Level 3 and 5!

V0404_09_00_43_0.text: When Right Hand Shark is on my field, I can summon this!

V0404_09_00_44_0.text: When it's revived from my Graveyard, its Level becomes 4!

V0404_09_00_45_0.text: Acid Golem is going to make me self-destruct...

V0404_11_01_00_0.text: I summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0404_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
I Xyz Summon!

V0404_13_00_00_0.text:
Cat Shark!
Come out and play!

V0404_37_00_00_0.text: I'll bring forth the most fearsome stronghold in the seas!

V0404_37_00_01_0.text: Let your roar create tidal waves in every ocean!

V0404_13_00_03_0.text: Welcome to the Duel, Black Ray Lancer!

V0404_13_00_04_0.text:
Dress for battle!
Full Armored Black Ray Lancer!

V0404_13_00_05_0.text:
The king of the deep!
Shark Caesar!

V0404_13_00_06_0.text:
I unleash the terror of both air and sea!
Aero Shark!

V0404_13_00_08_0.text:
Let's go!
Number 31: Embodiment of Punishment!

V0404_37_00_03_0.text: This denizen of the deep is thirsting for a feeding frenzy!

V0404_37_00_04_1.text: Swimming from the abyss is Number C32!

V0404_37_00_05_0.text: The land and the sea merge into a new life form!

V0404_13_00_11_0.text: Number 37: Hope Woven Dragon Spider Shark!

V0404_37_00_06_0.text: Purify chaos with your sacred water!

V0404_37_00_07_0.text: Number 94 is here to freeze the world in ice!

V0404_13_00_15_0.text: Gear up, Full Armored Crystalzero Lancer!

V0404_13_00_34_0.text: Rise from the deep, Depth Shark!

V0404_13_00_41_0.text:
Check out the largest monster in the seven seas!
Big Whale!

V0404_13_00_45_0.text: This super powerful Number has 3000 ATK!

V0404_19_00_04_0.text: Full Armored Black Ray Lancer! Attack!

V0404_19_00_31_0.text: Time to attack, Double Fin Shark!

V0404_19_00_45_0.text: Dissolve them to a goop, Acid Golem!

V0404_21_00_00_0.text: That's enough for you to feast on.

V0404_21_00_01_1.text: If you don't shape up, your next turn will be your last!

V0404_21_00_03_0.text: With that, I end my turn!

V0404_21_00_04_0.text: This doesn't look good for me...

V0404_21_00_05_0.text: There still has to be a way to win...

V0404_28_00_00_0.text: You learned the hard way not to mess with me!

V0404_28_00_02_0.text: Did you really think you could beat the best of the best?

V0404_28_00_04_0.text: You think this is a joke, Yuma?

V0404_28_00_04_1.text: If you won't Duel at the top of your game, you'll never win!

V0404_28_00_05_0.text: Come back when you're actually trying to win!

V0404_28_00_06_0.text: That's what you get for underestimating me!

V0404_28_00_07_0.text: I can say you're just as skilled as me.

V0404_28_00_07_1.text:
But I don't wanna lie!
Hahaha!
You'll never reach my level!

V0404_28_00_08_0.text: I knew I had to keep my guard up.

V0404_28_00_10_0.text: If you're trying to annoy me, you succeeded!

V0404_28_00_11_0.text: A Number may be powerful, but you're still just a card!

V0404_28_00_11_1.text: And if I know a card's effect, I know how to counter it!

V0404_28_00_12_0.text: You're like a school of fish - helpless when swimming solo!

V0404_28_00_13_0.text: I Duel alone because I don't need my crew to bail me out!

V0404_29_00_01_0.text: You don't know what you have until it's gone...

V0404_29_00_04_0.text: Looks like you're not as much of a loser as you used to be.

V0404_29_00_05_0.text: Your happy is making me not happy!

V0404_29_00_06_0.text: How many strategies does this guy have?

V0404_29_00_07_0.text:
You Dueled okay.
But I saw some weaknesses for next time.

V0404_29_00_08_0.text:
I lost to Quattro...
I couldn't get my revenge...

V0404_29_00_09_0.text: I won't... let you... control me...

V0404_29_00_10_0.text: Do what you want with me, but stay away from Rio.

V0404_33_00_00_0.text: Once I sink my teeth into you, I'll never let go!

V0404_34_00_02_0.text: You're back to the bottom of the food chain!

V0404_34_00_04_0.text: Ooh, so you DO know how to Duel.

V0404_34_00_05_0.text: Not bad... But not good either! Ha!

V0404_34_00_06_0.text: A shark never lets its prey escape!

V0404_34_00_07_0.text: There's a reason why everyone's afraid of the shark!

V0404_34_00_08_0.text: Summon your best monster! I'm ready for it!

V0404_34_00_09_0.text: Don't claim to be the King if you're not wearing the crown!

V0404_34_00_10_0.text: What's the point of a combo if you can't deal me damage?

V0404_36_00_00_0.text: This Duel is good as ours!

V0404_36_00_02_0.text:
Don't give up.
There's always an opening.

V0404_36_00_07_0.text: I don't think you need my help.

V0404_36_00_09_0.text: We're supposed to be a team, so play like you're in one.

V0404_36_00_10_0.text:
I don't need your help!
Ever!
